verbose_text: Importantly, although tm4sf18 mediated EC emergence and motility appeared to be VEGF dependent (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY C), disruption of ISV extension was not a consequence of reduced EC motility, as movement of emerging tm4sf18 -/- ECs was initially indistinguishable from that of WT, and stalling was only observed later in development (XREF_FIG C).
